Optional is just a way of not returning null
whenever u returning something which might exist or not then u can
return an optional back
and that's what most of the methods in the stream do.

 List.of(23,45,67,12).stream().filter(n->n%2==0).max((n1,n2)->Integer.compare(n1,n2))
$1 ==> Optional[12]

List.of(23,45,67).stream().filter(n->n%2==0).max((n1,n2)->Integer.compare(n1,n2))
$4 ==> Optional.empty

